episodes.title: Tehri
episodes.plot: In a sweet and sour tiff between mother-son, projecting the disappointments that both have against each other. The mother worries that her son is jobless and disregards her son fussing about the food not being served.

episodes.title: Hum Do Hamare Do
episodes.plot: Both the brothers fight over the volume of the television. Aman requests his mother to convince Annu to make his drawing for his practical exam, starting another argument.

episodes.title: Itwaar
episodes.plot: On a not so good early Sunday morning, Annu's mother wakes up to the alarm ringing. With the arrival of Sunday, most middle class families plan to make it special. How special would be the Sunday of Mishra family?

episodes.title: Batti Aa Gayi
episodes.plot: Aman enquires about Annu who hasn't returned home late. Annu's father is relaxed while awaiting him. Annu returns to only demand for a scooty, making up excuses for being late.

episodes.title: Tyohaar
episodes.plot: It's Raksha Bandhan, Shanti falls sick yet has to work all day. Annu shares his exam results with Aman, so he suggests him to run away. Shanti falls unconscious on hearing upon Annu's exam results.
